<plot>Robin, a young college girl, is enjoying a night at the movies with a friend, Leif. On her way back to her car she is hauled into a dark alley and raped. The Rapist forces her to choose between death or living with the violation. Robin chooses to live. Robin feels guilty for putting herself in the situation and does not tell anyone. Even in silence, she can't escape the choice she made and she draws away from everything and everybody. Robin can't live like this so returns to the alley to find the rapist and kill him. She hopes that will give her the peace she so desires.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?483270</url></doc>
